dct_title_s: Manshū Gomanbun no ichi Haisen Kokusan fukin
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Maps of Baiquan Xian and Keshan Xian vicinity (In Manchuria) showing villiages, towns, roads and vegetation.
LC copy stamped on: "Army Map Service Library"
Each sheet individually numbered, e.g. Dai 1gō.
Each sheet includes quadrangle location map.
